  pytrainer-1.10.0.ebuild,
  +files/pytrainer-1.10.0-workaround_relative_path_breakage.patch:
  Fix path breakage with latest python-exec implementation.

  03 Jul 2013; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> pytrainer-1.10.0.ebuild:
  Use $PYTHON_USEDEP, where possible.

  08 May 2013; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> pytrainer-1.9.1.ebuild,
  pytrainer-1.10.0.ebuild:
  Use $PYTHON_USEDEP, where possible.

